BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Science Factory
X-SOURCE-URL:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T150000
DTSTAMP:20260328T230356
CREATED:20260223T191059Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260223T191059Z
UID:10002693-1775901600-1775919600@lancastersciencefactory.org
SUMMARY:Video Game Day
DESCRIPTION:Game on! \nWe’re partnering with the Lancaster Rec Esports program for a day of video game design and play! Compete in popular games like Super Smash Brothers™ and Mario Kart™. Players can test their skills\, cheer on friends\, and experience the excitement of esports in a welcoming\, supportive environment.\n\nVisitors of all ages can also participate in our Play for Impact Video Game Design Workshops. Participants will design\, develop\, and test their own video game using Scratch\, a block-based programming tool.\n\nStay tuned for more video game fun as the event gets closer!  This event is presented free with admission.  \nClick here to purchase tickets in advance for April 11th. Tickets will also be sold at the door.\nWhy Video Games and Esports?\nEsports is one of the fastest-growing career fields in the world\, offering opportunities not only as players but also in areas like computer programming\, digital art\, broadcasting\, marketing\, and game development. Colleges and universities\, including local institutions\, now offer esports teams\, scholarships\, and academic pathways that turn a passion for gaming into meaningful careers.
URL:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/event/video-game-day/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Science Factory\, 454 New Holland Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Educational Programs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/wp-content/uploads/3_Video-Game-Day-Event-Banner.png
GEO:40.0461822;-76.2963319
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=The Lancaster Science Factory 454 New Holland Ave Lancaster PA 17602 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=454 New Holland Ave:geo:-76.2963319,40.0461822
END:VEVENT
